name: Pongs Squad - Blakmet
description:
Pongs Squad is a group of criminals from an unknown country. They are scattered in various parts of the world due to a dispute between their captain and vice-captain.

Budi Tarno is the spy of this group. He was nicknamed Blakmet. There's nothing special about him. There is a magnet in his body which causes his body to be surrounded by iron. His eyes were exposed to too much x-ray so that they turned into wireframes. Currently, he is hiding somewhere in Indonesia.
